OL,3,CMahmood warns of stark choices for
OL,4,Cprison reform to ensure 'worthy' system
OL,6,FThe Justice Secretary warned of having
OL,7,Fto make "stark choices" in relation to
OL,8,Fprison reform to ensure a criminal
OL,9,Fjustice system "worthy of the name",
OL,10,Fit has been reported.
OL,12,FPlans for long-term reform are
OL,13,Fexpected to be introduced following
OL,14,Fthe independent sentencing review,
OL,15,Fwhich is due to be published on
OL,16,FThursday ` which could include a
OL,17,Fscheme through which private companies
OL,18,Femploy offenders but reduce their
OL,19,Fwages and give the money to victims,
OL,20,Faccording to The Times.
