OL,3,CMahmood warns of stark choices for
OL,4,Cprison reform to ensure 'worthy' system
OL,6,FThe review, led by former justice
OL,7,Fsecretary David Gauke, is exploring
OL,8,Foptions to hand offenders tougher
OL,9,Fpunishments outside prison, while
OL,10,Fmaking sure there is space to jail the
OL,11,Fmost dangerous criminals.
OL,13,FShabana Mahmood told The Times: "This
OL,14,Fissue and this crisis and what it
OL,15,Fmeans for people all over the country,
OL,16,Fit's far above party politics.
OL,18,F"I appreciate these are very, very
OL,19,Fdifficult decisions. I find making
OL,20,Fthese decisions difficult for myself.
OL,26,@uD@aOUzD@AOU
