OL,3,CMahmood warns of stark choices for
OL,4,Cprison reform to ensure 'worthy' system
OL,6,F"I've got to consider the whole of the
OL,7,Fsystem, how to do right by everybody
OL,8,Fand we're facing some very, very stark
OL,9,Fchoices.
OL,11,F"It's a horrible reality to be in. It
OL,12,Fshows the scale of the terrible
OL,13,Finheritance that the Conservative
OL,14,FParty left behind.
