OL,3,CMahmood warns of stark choices for
OL,4,Cprison reform to ensure 'worthy' system
OL,6,F"But this is where we have a duty, we
OL,7,Fhave to act in the nation's best
OL,8,Finterest, we have to make sure that
OL,9,Fthere is a criminal justice system
OL,10,Fworthy of the name. We have to make
OL,11,Fsure we don't run out of prison
OL,12,Fplaces."
OL,14,FChanges could include allowing well-
OL,15,Fbehaved prisoners to be released after
OL,16,Fserving only a third of their
OL,17,Fsentences and ending jail terms for
OL,18,Foffenders sentenced to less than one
OL,19,Fyear in prison, according to The Times.
