OL,3,CMahmood warns of stark choices for
OL,4,Cprison reform to ensure 'worthy' system
OL,6,FSuch offenders will reportedly serve
OL,7,Fcommunity sentences, which could
OL,8,Finvolve filling potholes and clearing
OL,9,Ffly-tipping areas.
OL,11,FThe paper also said the Government is
OL,12,Ftalking to private companies about a
OL,13,Fscheme that would employ criminals but
OL,14,Freduce their wages and donate the
OL,15,Fmoney to victims.
OL,17,FLatest Ministry of Justice (MoJ)
OL,18,Ffigures published on Monday show the
OL,19,Fnumber of inmates in jails has risen
OL,20,Fby 2,485 since December 30.
