OL,3,CMahmood warns of stark choices for
OL,4,Cprison reform to ensure 'worthy' system
OL,6,FIt comes as the Government announced
OL,7,Ffurther emergency plans to release
OL,8,Fsome criminals on recall earlier to
OL,9,Ffree up around 1,400 prison places.
OL,11,FIt is hoped the move, which sparked a
OL,12,Fbacklash over concerns for victims and
OL,13,Fpublic safety, will "buy time" before
OL,14,Fsentencing reforms are expected to
OL,15,Ftake effect next spring.
OL,17,FLegislation to bring in the changes is
OL,18,Fexpected to be introduced in the
OL,19,Fcoming weeks.
