OL,3,CMahmood warns of stark choices for
OL,4,Cprison reform to ensure 'worthy' system
OL,6,FThe MoJ's permanent secretary, Amy
OL,7,FRees, warned last week that, based on
OL,8,Fthe current trajectory, the prison
OL,9,Fpopulation rises by 3,000 each year
OL,10,Fand is now expected to hit zero
OL,11,Fcapacity for male prisons by November
OL,12,Fthis year.
OL,14,FMs Mahmood also announced that three
OL,15,Fnew prisons will be built, starting
OL,16,Fthis year, as part of a "record prison
OL,17,Fexpansion", after securing a capital
OL,18,Finvestment of #4.7 billion.
